         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085"><!-- p3l5-r15 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Hd1e108">Rubrica 15</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De minis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>
      ¶ De minis. ¶ Rubrica. 18<!--dbcheck -->
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>SAlomon in prouerbiis.
      <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>c. 12. <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e127">Fatuus
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>Istatim vidicat iram suam. Qui autem
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/>dissimulat iniuriam calidus est.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e135">
               <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e139">¶ Cronica de nugis philosophorum. c. 8 scilice
        <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>de chylone. Chylo lacedemoniis. qui fuit
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/>vnus de septem sapiententibus iubebat non esse
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>minandum cuique. Muliebre namque. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e150">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e154">¶ Oratius in poetria. Nec semper feriet qui
        <lb ed="#V" n="24" break="no"/>cunque minabitur arcus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e160">
               <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e164">¶ Seneca tragediarum in medea. c. 3 Ira
        <lb ed="#V" n="26" break="no"/>que tegitur nocet. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e170"> /
      <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e172"> Idem in prouerbiis. Lo
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>quax inimicus minus quam taciturnus offendit </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e178">
               <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e182">¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum: libro. 4. c. 49.
        <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>Plerumque denunciata comminatio plus efficit
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/>quam pena componat. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e190">
               <lb ed="#V" n="31"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e194">¶ Gregorius in pastorali. c. 39. Plerunque
        <lb ed="#V" n="32"/>nimis taciti cum nonnulla iniusta patiun
        <lb ed="#V" n="33" break="no"/>tur: eo in acriorem dolorem prodeunt quo
        <lb ed="#V" n="34"/>ea qui sustinent non loquuntur. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e204">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e208">¶ Uersificator fabularum esopi. 26 Sepe
        <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>minus faciunt homines qui magna minantur </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e215">
               <lb ed="#V" n="37"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e219">¶ Baldo. 9 fabula. Uis metuenda parum: vox
        <lb ed="#V" n="38"/>est vbi multa minarum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e225">
               <lb ed="#V" n="39"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e229">¶ henricus samariensis. l. 2. Dicta minus
        <lb ed="#V" n="40"/>sint: facta magis: sis parcus in minis.
        <lb ed="#V" n="41"/>Parcus in obprobriis largus ad omne decus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-d1e237">
               <lb ed="#V" n="42"/>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d64085-Qd1e241">¶ Prouerbia vulgaria.
        <lb ed="#V" n="43"/>Manace non e lance. <!--195.xml-->
      </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
